			<h1><span class="less"><a href="index.html">SLE 2018</a> paper:</span><br><i>Constraint-based run-time state migration for live modeling</i></h1>
			<h2><a href="../profile/UlyanaTikhonova.html">Ulyana Tikhonova</a>, <a href="../profile/JoukeStoel.html">Jouke Stoel</a>, <a href="../profile/TijsvanderStorm.html">Tijs van der Storm</a>, <a href="../profile/ThomasDegueule.html">Thomas Degueule</a></h2>
